high_descs: pick up sharp knife from island
wash and remove knife from sink
turn left to face drawers under counters
put knife in drawer near dishwasher
Turn left and walk around to the far side of the kitchen island.
Pick up the large metal knife off of the kitchen island.
Turn right and walk over to the counter, then turn left and walk up to the sink.
Wash the large metal knife in the sink and then pick it back up.
Turn left and walk forward towards the microwave then stop.
Open the second drawer from the bottom to the left of the dishwasher and put the clean large knife inside, then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean large knife in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn left for two steps, turn right for two steps, turn left for six steps, turn left for six steps and face the kitchen island.
Pick up the big knife with the yellow handle from the island.
Turn right for five steps, turn left for three steps, and then turn right to face the sink.
Put the knife in the sink, standing up with the tip down to the left of the spatula handle and near the silver plate, turn on the water for a few seconds and then take out the knife.
Turn left, take one step and stop.
Open the third drawer down to the left of the dishwasher and put the knife in the drawer and shut it.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean knife in the third drawer.
